    "Our results raise questions about using LLMs for emotion-related NLP tasks.",
    "They emphasize the importance of examining and improving LLMs' fairness and inclusiveness.",
    "We advocate for more interdisciplinary collaboration to build upon prior research in this domain.",
    "Closed-weight models like GPT-4 present a challenge in terms of reproducibility, as we do not know when (or how) they are updated.",
    "Consequently, their responses may change regardless of temperature settings."
